  "text": "Passaging of C. albicans strain P60002 Ninety-six individual colonies of strain P60002 were cultured in liquid medium by serial passaging for 18 days. Cells were cultured in 900 µl yeast extract, peptone and dextrose (YPD) medium at [CITATION_1] C on a shaking platform. Every 24 h, 15 µl was transferred to 885 µl of fresh YPD medium.",
